# Documents

This project uses `full` document mode.

## Directory Rules

- `requirements/`: requirements, scope, boundaries, task breakdowns
- `designs/`: product design, technical design, implementation proposals
- `deliveries/`: implementation notes, verification results, delivery summaries
- `evolution/`: long-term evolution, rule changes, version notes
- `standards/ai-collaboration/`: project-specific AI collaboration rules

All formal documents should be routed into those directories.
